title: DOOM PATROL Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: This show really caught me by surprise. Huge production value, characters I cared about, and it was just plain'ole fun! What did you guys think?
Doom Patrol and The Umbrella Academy are simply amazing shows. People with superhuman abilities dealing with human problems, I love it.

The butts are looooose. 😅😂
I love Doom Patrol, best DC show.
Mr nobody is one of the best villians that dc has imo I loved how his character was portrayed he was the high light of the show

This show is deep at least some episode are.

Poor Jane.   It really gives you a victim personall  perspective of victims who suffered sexual abuse by a parent.
description:
In this video I break down and explain the ending to season one of DC Universe's "Doom Patrol". Who is Dorothy Spinner and what will happen to Crazy Jane, Robot Man, Elasti-Girl, Mr. Nobody, Cyborg, and Larry!?
